{"tid":1638184,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【女仔】如何避免俾狗咬？","createTime":"2019-10-08T08:36:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T12:29:05.000Z","uid":307068,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"549c03ff25148f2e0fd5c89f18b6162d58d90a65","tid":1638184,"uid":307068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:36:29.000Z","msg":"樓主讀過性別研究, 好明白咩叫身體政治<br />\n熟讀free the nipples等等的social movements都係想提高awareness<br />\n但有時抗爭都需要識得<strong><ins>保護自己</ins></strong><br />\n呢幾日見唔少女仔冇乜準備<br />\n班狗又愈來愈中意淨係咬女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果你知道自己肯定唔夠狗打<br />\n又跑得唔夠快<br />\n希望下面的practical tips可以令你面對狗冇咁驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nPS: 以下tips 未必適合蔥蔥 同埋 full gear 的你<br />\n我但不妨參考下<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">外表:</span></span><br />\n- 有幾樣衰扮幾衰, 真係唔好化妝同扮靚, 等佢睇你唔上眼<br />\n- 帶定一副假眼鏡, 冇度數的<br />\n- 扎頭髮<br />\n- 就算冇黑色帽, 都一定要帶帽<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">衣著:</span></span><br />\n- 唔好著短褲同背心, 我知好熱, 如果想落場的時候著短褲, 可以考試著長短二合一行山褲<br />\n一拉拉鍊, 可以即時變做長褲<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\">- 唔。好。再。著。運。動。短。褲。落。場！！</span></ins></strong><br />\n- 掛件淺色衫係頸, 方便即刻變身<br />\n我知大家對黑色都有情意結，亦都係抗爭標誌<br />\n但係你知自己跑唔郁，又何必要俾狗標籤去攻擊？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">行為：</span></span><br />\n如果兜口兜面見到狗, 而你又啱啱變身／或未變得切身, 建議可以做以下野幫自己抽離：<br />\n- 暫時唔好睇tg, 開其他app睇其他野<br />\n- 如果要對狗發洩情緒，唔好俾機會佢以言入罪，嘗試講「嘩～～～」<br />\n- 開openrice 同你隔離個個「搵食」<br />\n- 開巴士app google map 搵下路<br />\n- 就算唔食都要買定包煙，扮街坊, 啲狗一衝過嚟掉曬啲裝備, 即刻點煙<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">重點: 你唔需要緊張, 面部彊硬。話俾自己知: 你頭先咩都冇做過!!!!!!</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n精神係: 必要時出賣自己<br />\n唔係出賣別人, 係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">自己</span></strong></span>, 扮唔係夢遊, 只係經過, 食花生, 或者街坊<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最最最緊要：千祈唔好自己一個落單!! </span></strong></ins><br />\n就算你真係自己一個落左樓下，係周圍搵幾條男仔扮男／朋友<br />\n我知係好冇骨氣, 好怕羞<br />\n但如果<ins><span style=\"color: red;\">馬蹄露</span></ins>都可以係俾人打之後, 十指緊扣拖實個外國記者<br />\n你！都！一！定！做！得！出！<br />\n（頭盔）我完全唔係reinforce緊男權，唔係話男人就一定有用<br />\n但你要記住，對面班狗係冇人性，冇學識，要用返佢地個腦去應付佢地<br />\n<br />\n如有補充<br />\n歡迎大家集思廣益 分享經驗<br />\n第一次出post sorry for 1999"},{"pid":"0381ba174a26d9e7627b889f79f997733d84e42d","tid":1638184,"uid":307068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:37:02.000Z","msg":"自推10"},{"pid":"85fe5996031f2629f63561d00bdf63da88c203e7","tid":1638184,"uid":307068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:37:14.000Z","msg":"自推9"},{"pid":"305251a340f55ff92553b4dfde245d0c26c6aeef","tid":1638184,"uid":307068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:37:28.000Z","msg":"自推8"},{"pid":"5068e8c758ad89c3624a3cbf46ee5368eca18145","tid":1638184,"uid":307068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:37:38.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"1f3b3be30c4a41a3469e1eedba892a9814739232","tid":1638184,"uid":307068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:37:48.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"9fb2cb150c50bf9bdd5c3dc93c9999ba84e3d3a2","tid":1638184,"uid":307068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:38:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bab596db4cd1fdefc4cc8c9f0acf85d747f62a8","tid":1638184,"uid":307068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:38:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec5c86e899279628f7b5bf8c29093074a14dcc8f","tid":1638184,"uid":321618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:39:04.000Z","msg":"真 落單左真係幾驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8f70d7a02b28c6662f235bd8baa16713fa65ad8","tid":1638184,"uid":197561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:39:29.000Z","msg":"但如果馬蹄露都可以係俾人打之後, 十指緊扣拖實個外國記者<br />\n你！都！一！定！做！得！出！笑咗<br />\n<br />\n幫推"},{"pid":"eaa79c522e56f418c47d1d15c270f43f4cc8537b","tid":1638184,"uid":307068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:39:32.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"a77a9e93181dce4518d445dd48c02b15be66fdb5","tid":1638184,"uid":151890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:41:50.000Z","msg":"扮街坊要食煙/點煙？<br />\n屌你啦 <br />\n最憎煙鏟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55a17536abf2d3823945002bc8ba2ef6649b0095","tid":1638184,"uid":279810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:52:10.000Z","msg":"宜家出動到掳人禁固, 唔好單獨出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6cf2a8ccf03364b2b7e4e9cb07824d855aa237a","tid":1638184,"uid":307068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:56:10.000Z","msg":"推到所有絲打見到為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10f338a5661d20b0d63de9d1fccbb265201c4134","tid":1638184,"uid":307794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:43:31.000Z","msg":"推！！！！"},{"pid":"13353bd87d7ec1270daed972f319370ee9f9d725","tid":1638184,"uid":307068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:43:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">見到多左人講女手足<br />\n大家一定要背熟以上tips呀！</span>"},{"pid":"59ca62535eaabd45c5159aeeb4ba1fe8fcb2333f","tid":1638184,"uid":114226,"like"